## 1. Objective

Replicate the Keytec "Drupal & KI: Zukunft gestalten" blog landing page 1:1 within the Designbook environment. The page is a service-style landing page with a valentine-themed hero featuring a multi-layer SVG collage illustration, rich body content sections, a 3-column related articles grid, a contact CTA with a contact person card, and full shell (header/footer). The workflow `/debo-design-screen blog` orchestrates this through 9 sequential steps, culminating in a complete visual page design viewable in Storybook.

